    <description>Handles Invoice Net Amount == null

Filtered transaction types of &#39;On-Hold&#39;, &#39;Needs Review&#39;, &#39;Canceled&#39;, &amp; &#39;Failed&#39; out of the query so the balance paid/due calculations are accurate.

Sets Opportunity Deposit Refund Date if the deposit was partially/fully refunded</description>
    <formulas>
        <name>BalanceDue_Calculated</name>
        <dataType>Currency</dataType>
        <expression>{!Get_Invoice.Net_Amount__c} - {!Get_Invoice.Balance_Paid__c}</expression>
        <scale>2</scale>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
